1. *Zaboravili* smo da je večeras sastanak. (We forgot that there is a meeting tonight.)
2. Oni su *zaboravili* da obave posao. (They forgot to do the job.)
3. *Zaboravila* sam da treba da dođem na vreme. (I forgot to come on time.)
4. Nismo *zaboravili* da postoje problemi. (We didn't forget that there are problems.)
5. *Zaboravio* sam da zapamtim broj. (I forgot to remember the number.)